  "stem": "<figure class=\"table\"><table border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>x</th><th>f(x)</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>-1</td><td>16</td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>1/16</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>1/256</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>For the exponential function f, the table shows four values of x and their corresponding values of f(x). Which equation defines f?</p>",
